# Privacy Policy for qrcodesmakeyou

**Effective Date:** 23/08/2024

## 1. Information We Collect

### a. Personal Information
We collect your name and email address, which are stored in our database. Thay are provided to us when you login via a third-party service (e.g., Spotify).

### b. Non-Personal Information
Our app does not collect and information about the computer from which you access it.
Our app does not store information about the qrcodes that you generate. All qrcode generation is done on the "client-side", that is to say: on your computer.

### c. Third-Party Services
We Vercel services, such as analytics, that may collect and process some non-personal data. Third-parties have their own privacy policies, and we encourage you to review them.

## 2. How We Use Your Information

Your information is only used to programatically provide you with qrcode suggestions, it is not viewed by people, or used for data analysis.

## 3. Data Retention

We retain the non-personal data we collect for as long as it is necessary for the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy. Personal data (if collected voluntarily) will be retained only for as long as is necessary to fulfill the purpose for which it was provided or as required by law.

Importantly, the data about qrcodes you generate does not leave your own computer, therefore we cannot retain it.

## 4. Data Security

We take appropriate security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of your data. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

## 5. Sharing of Information

We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share non-personal information with third-party service providers to help us operate the app, improve its functionality, or for analytics purposes.

## 6. Your Choices and Rights

You have the right to:
- Request access to any personal data we may hold about you.
- Request that we correct or delete any personal information you have provided to us.
- Withdraw consent where we are relying on it to process your data.

To exercise these rights, please contact us at qrcodesmakeyou@josephabbey.dev.

## 7. Childrenâ€™s Privacy

Our app is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we become aware that we have collected personal information from a child under 13, we will take steps to delete such information as soon as possible.

Our app can be used by children under the age of 13, if they do not sign in. This means that no data is collected.

## 8. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page, with an updated "Effective Date." We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically.

## 9. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:
- Email: qrcodesmakeyou@josephabbey.dev
